Package: NEONiso
Type: Package
Title: Calibrate and plot NEON Atmospheric Isotope Data
Version: 0.4.0.9000
Author: Rich Fiorella
Maintainer: Rich Fiorella <rich.fiorella@utah.edu>
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.5.0)
Description: This package provides functions for downloading,
    calibrating, and analyzing atmospheric isotope data bundled
    into the eddy covariance data products of the National Ecological
    Observatory Network (NEON). In this version, calibration tools
    are provided for only the carbon isotope products. Tools for
    calibrating water isotope products are under development.
License: GPL-3 + file LICENSE
BugReports: https://github.com/SPATIAL-Lab/NEONiso/issues
URL: https://github.com/SPATIAL-Lab/NEONiso
Encoding: UTF-8
